### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "name": "John Doe"
}

### Login with credentials
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Get protected profile (Replace YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN with actual token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

### Refresh token (Replace YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN with actual refresh token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### Logout (Replace YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN with actual token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

### Error Scenarios ###

### 1. Register with invalid email
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "invalid-email",
    "password": "123456",
    "name": "Test"
}

### 2. Login with wrong password
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 3. Access protected endpoint without token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json

### Using Environment Variables ###
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@email = test@test.com
@password = test123
@name = Test User
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN

### Register with variables
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}",
    "name": "{{name}}"
}

### Login with variables
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Profile with variable token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Refresh with variable token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Logout with variable token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json